originalText.text:
Sere is a perfect agent who always puts clients interests first. Buying an apartment is always a stress, but she makes buyers life easier in every aspect. If you follow her recommendations on lawyers and financing, you can be sure the purchase process will go smoothly and be completed successfully.

Our case was complicated, however everything was resolved and we moved in just as planned.

I highly recommend Sere to everyone looking for a new apartment.

originalText.text: Sere came highly recommended to us by a close friend and thank goodness they did! She understood exactly what we were looking for in our new home in Manhattan. Great location, a chic outdoor space, elegant & clean design. Extraordinary service all the way from creating lists of places to see, to the bid process, to the mortgage and even to the roller blinds and the furniture! If you want a completely seamless real estate shopping experience, look no farther than the fabulous Sere.

originalText.text:
Sere was hands down the best person for the job to help me find my apartment in NYC. Here’s what you can expect with Sere:
- extremely professional: Sere was on time for all of our showings and had all of our appointments added to my calendar ahead of time. She listened to what I was looking for and sent me tons of apartments to review before booking showings.
- always on your side: When we toured places, I felt like Sere understood what I was looking for in a home and represented me and my needs without any hesitation.
- no fuss: Sere and I clocked about 20K steps one day looking at apartments up and down nyc. She never complained about my endless questions and made me feel comfortable no matter what my concern was
- above and beyond: I couldn’t actually see the place I decided to rent and Sere insisted in showing me every detail of the building to make sure I felt good about my decision.

Sere treats her clients like family and I am so lucky I had Sere’s help in finding my new home. I recommend Sere 100%!!

originalText.text: Sere has been instrumental for my home-buying process. As a first-time home buyer, I really appreciated Sere's kindness and patience, especially as she helped me navigate the process of applying to a co-op building. Sere and her team were highly knowledgeable about the housing market. Sere is extremely responsive, compassionate, and skillful with coordinating every step of the buying process, and made a complicated process much easier. I would highly recommend working with her!
